Hello everyone who reads my thread, I need 2 coders to accompany me making a new server based on cheez 78 source. I already have complete canoes and stuff, and im on the way to developing more. Do you wanna help me with it? SIGN UP! ITS FREE :D!
Goals: Make a more realistic server Keep the server up-to-date Make every skill work. Make people have fun Making an easy-to-modify source, so people can use this very easily ;)
If you want to participate add me on MSN or email me on: xerox79@gmail.com
Thanks in advance, ~System79
